								<code>
								  &lt;img src="http://www.tatango.com/sms-marketing-tools/sms-qr-code-image?keyword=<span id="urlKeyword"></span>&amp;shortcode=<span id="urlShortcode"></span>" alt="Powered by Tatango SMS Marketing" /&gt;
